text: Chulpan () is a rural locality (a village) in Satyyevsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 24 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 5 km from Satyyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Chulpan, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
